---
import Avatar from "../ui/Avatar.astro";
import guy from "../../images/devs/guy.png";
---

<section class="my-20 px-4 md:px-6 text-foreground">
  <div
    class="flex flex-col space-y-2 lg:col-start-3 lg:col-span-8 lg:space-y-4 max-w-[680px] m-auto"
  >
    <blockquote
      class="text-lg leading-loose font-serif italic text-foreground border-l-2 border-border pl-3 sm:text-xl md:pl-4 md:text-2xl"
    >
      "As someone with a strong JavaScript background and very little Rust, I
      did not expect this book to make me so productive at writing Lambda
      functions using Rust. It definitely accelerated my path to production and
      the gains are insane!"
    </blockquote>
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 lg:justify-start">
      <Avatar
        class="w-12 h-12"
        image={guy}
        fallback="GA"
        alt="Guy Ackchyually, Junior Cloud Developer"
      />
      <div class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        â€” Guy Ackchyually, Cloud Developer
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
